(13, 5, 'Resumen El objetivo de este taller es que los empr...', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><div><div><h2>Resumen&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><p>El objetivo de este taller es que los emprendedores conozcan principios de diseño que les permitan crear publicaciones que capturen la atención de los actuales y los potenciales clientes, utilizando el programa/APP gratuita Canva.</p><h2>Temario</h2><ul id=\"block-7006b7c7-e4fa-4822-b721-81638d05c161\"><li>Importancia de la imagen</li><li>Aplicando el branding en Redes Sociales</li><li>Diseño y emociones</li><li>Crear diseños en Canva</li></ul></div><div><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"682\" height=\"1023\" data-attachment-id=\"2269\" data-permalink=\"https://fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/lessons/taller-3-disena-con-canva/3-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-1.png?fit=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"682,1023\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"3-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-1.png?fit=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-1.png?fit=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-1.png?resize=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacio