(14, 5, 'Resumen Los participantes podrán crear y optimizar...', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><div><div><h2>Resumen&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</h2><p>Los participantes podrán crear y optimizar su cuenta de Instagram destinada a la promoción de su negocio, conociendo las diferentes herramientas de las que dispone la plataforma para su posicionamiento dentro de esta red social.</p><h2>Temario</h2><ul id=\"block-7006b7c7-e4fa-4822-b721-81638d05c161\"><li>Ventajas de una Cuenta Empresa</li><li>Publicaciones e Historias</li><li>La magia de los Reels</li><li>Cómo hacer un catálogo en Instagram</li></ul></div><div><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"682\" height=\"1023\" data-attachment-id=\"2278\" data-permalink=\"https://fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/lessons/taller-4-instagram/4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4.png?fit=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"682,1023\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4.png?fit=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4.png?fit=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindependiente.cl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4.png?resize=682%2C1023&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/fundacionvidaindep